dc_title_s: Tabula Mexicae et Floridae: terrarum Anglicarum, et anteriorum Americae Insularum, item cursuum et circuituum fluminis Mississippi dicti.
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Shows what is now the United States, Mexico, Central America and the Caribbean. 1 map: hand col.; 46 x 60 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
